# ENTITY::RESET_PICKUP_ENTITY_GLOW

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Revert entity alpha override and restart pickup glow.

Similar to RESET_ENTITY_ALPHA
